05/06/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- The United States would like to see Albania integrated into the EU and NATO, according to US State Department desk officer in Albania Lisa Gregory. On Wednesday (4 June), she met with Albania's Parliamentary Speaker Servet Pellumbi in Tirana. Pellumbi briefed Gregory on the activities of the parliament over the past year. He said Albanian authorities remain committed to anti-crime measures and enhancing global security while helping to rebuild Iraq. (BBC, ATA - 04/06/03)
